utimensat.2
    Goldwyn Rodrigues
        Immutable flag returns EPERM
            Linux kernel commit 337684a1746f "fs: return EPERM on immutable
            inode" changed the return value of the utimensat(2) from -EACCES
            to -EPERM in case of an immutable flag.

